      "side": 1,
      "message": "I think asm/ptrace-abi.h defines the raw system call interface while sys/ptrace.h defines the libc interface. The glibc ptrace wrapper requires its request arguments to be enum __ptrace_request and re-defines many of the requests from asm/ptrace-abi.h, but is missing PTRACE_GET_THREAD_AREA.",
